attributes.description: JSW Steel is primarily engaged in the business of manufacture and sale of Iron and Steel Products.[1] It is the flagship business of the diversified, US$ 23 billion JSW Group.The Group has interests in energy, infrastructure, cement, paints, sports, and venture capital.[2]
